Document Dependencies 
Technical dependencies: Platform upgrades, API changes required External dependencies: Third-party integrations, partnerships Team dependencies: Design handoff, data pipeline work 
Example: 
CODE markdown 516CHARS
Document Open Questions 
Unresolved decisions: Areas requiring discovery or discussion 
Example: 
